WEBVTT

00:05.812 --> 00:07.002
Here's what happened.

00:07.207 --> 00:11.119
{\pos(192,230)}You were in the middle of a very messy,
very expensive divorce,

00:11.369 --> 00:13.293
{\pos(192,230)}and you wanted to get rid of your wife.

00:13.650 --> 00:16.258
That is absurd.
Do I have to listen to this?

00:16.321 --> 00:19.684
- Yes, you do.
- What you needed was an alibi.

00:20.313 --> 00:22.664
<i>First, you ordered
a two-ton slab of marble.</i>

00:22.883 --> 00:26.247
<i>Then you went to work, but you
weren't sculpting just another statue.</i>

00:26.490 --> 00:29.884
<i>You were sculpting an alibi,
a perfect alibi.</i>

00:29.947 --> 00:32.546
<i>You had it all worked out,</i>
down to the last

00:32.665 --> 00:35.235
- details
- Hold it! Don't say another word.

00:35.450 --> 00:37.802
Excuse me,
sir, this is a private conversation.

00:37.865 --> 00:40.424
Yeah, this conversation's over,
unless you want to talk to me,

00:40.487 --> 00:42.666
but I cannot promise
that I would listen, detective.

00:42.752 --> 00:44.554
- And you are?
- I'm Harrison Powell.

00:44.617 --> 00:47.240
I'm Mr. Gildea's Attorney.
I just moved up from Los Angeles.

00:47.303 --> 00:49.778
And you must be Mr. Adrian Monk.

00:50.120 --> 00:52.695
I saw your profile on in Focus.
Very impressive.

00:52.826 --> 00:54.776
Thank you.
I was just explaing to...

00:54.839 --> 00:58.220
Why don't you tell it to the judge?
We're denying everything categorically.

00:58.297 --> 01:01.518
Have a nice day. Come on. Let's go. You
look like a man who could use a drink.

01:02.096 --> 01:04.848
Evan, let's go.
They can't keep you here. It's okay.

01:07.815 --> 01:09.030
Harrison, it's too late.

01:09.093 --> 01:11.468
They know everything.
They have all this evidence against me.

01:11.531 --> 01:13.744
No, they have no evidence against you.
They have nothing,

01:13.807 --> 01:16.087
Okay? You're an innocent man
that's been unjustly accused.

01:16.150 --> 01:18.335
And I'm gonna prove all
that when we get to court.

01:18.398 --> 01:21.652
Harrison, it's Adrian Monk.
He's never lost a case in his life.

01:21.718 --> 01:23.841
Well, neither have i.
This'll be great.

